      "notes": "Tauri + Vanilla JS template. Rust crate at src-tauri/. Frontend at src-web/. Root-level tooling owned by the Tauri template chain — do not touch. Toolchain via mise.toml.",
      "targets": [
        {
          "path": "src-tauri",
